com.yahoo.persistence.spi

Class Selection

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yahoo.persistence.spi.Selection

  • public class Selection
extends Object
    Class used when iterating to represent a selection of entries to be returned. This class is likely to be replaced by a more generic selection AST in the near future.
